    section#feats.s-services.light-gray
      .polluxi-right.polluxi: img(src="/images/NOT-xmaspol.png" data-aos='fade-right')
      .row.section-header(data-aos='fade-up')
        .col-full
          h3.subhead Pollux's feats
          h1.display-1 Pollux is novelty-oriented , not your regular "multipurpose" bot
      // end section-header
      .row(data-aos='fade-up')
        .col-full
          p.lead
            | Bots tend to be clunkered with all sorts of commands summing up to a bazillion unique ultrafun commands for everything. 
            | Even though havin a lot of commands is good so it saves you from adding 5 different bots just to achieve specific functions. It also means they're jack of all trades, but master of none.
            | We have enough music bots, enough moderation bots, enough bots in general.
            | What Pollux tries to achieve is master what these do poorly and did little or nothing to improve. Because<i> it just works</i>. 
      // end about-desc
      .row.services-list.block-1-3.block-m-1-2.block-tab-full
        .col-block.service-item(data-aos='fade-down-right' data-aos-offset='500')
          .service-icon.service-icon--brand-identity
            //i.icon-tv
            i.far.fa-gem
          .service-text
            h3.h4 Solid and dynamic economy system
            p Pollux has three internal currencies: Jades dust, worthless but useful for crafting. Rubine gems, the main currency which can buy anything if you have enough of them. And Sapphire shards, which are the premium currency available only during events or for donators. 
            //ul 
              li Jade Dust: These greenish gems has little to no value, but are useful in crafting cool items to be used with other functionalities!
              li Rubine Gems: Our main and public currency, everything can be bought with it. Prices of cosmetics can fluctuate depending on Rubines volume, you can also exchange them for other bots' currencies!
              li Sapphire Shards: The ultimate premium currency, these can only be obtained in really rare ocasions like Events or when you get your daily bonus 200x in a row. Donators receive a bunch of them monthly depending on their contribution, they can also be bought sepparately with smaller donations <a href="/store">here</a>!
        .col-block.service-item(data-aos='fade-down' data-aos-offset='500')
          .service-icon.service-icon--illustration
            i.fas.fa-cubes 
          .service-text
            h3.h4 A ton of cosmetics.. with Lootboxes!
            p Pollux has over 1000 options of cosmetics to decorate your PPC (Pollux Profile Card), you can do infinite combinations of Backgrounds, Medals, Flairs, Stickers and on top of thet set a unique accent color to it. All of these items can be obtained wither from one of the Rubine shops, or from Lootboxes that are dropped every so often in servers. 
        .col-block.service-item(data-aos='fade-down-left' data-aos-offset='500')
          .service-icon.service-icon--web-design
            i.fas.fa-paint-brush 
          .service-text
            h3.h4 Original concepts and artwork
            p Unlike 99.9% of all bots out there, Pollux was created originally to fit the role as your virtual maid, with a lot of tiny details, personality, and featuring several pieces of artwork. In addition to Pollux herself, there's an ever growing roster of side-characters with some degree of depth to add more color to things like events, for extra delight of roleplay-driven users.
            
        .col-block.service-item(data-aos='fade-up-right')
          .service-icon.service-icon--product-strategy
            i.fa.fa-retweet 
          .service-text
            h3.h4 Cross-server and cross-bot feats
            p Pollux doesn't limit herself to the island of your server, or even to herself. Pollux can exchange her currencies with other bots that participate in the Discoin service, like DiscordTel, Dice, and Elite Looter, to name a few. You can also import your Profile Data from Pollux to other bots like Loritta. 
            //p Some of Pollux's features are made to increase cross-server interaction
            
        .col-block.service-item(data-aos='fade-up')
          .service-icon.service-icon--ui-design
            i.fa.fa-crosshairs 
          .service-text
            h3.h4 We take your fun seriously
            p Also unlike 99.9% of all bots over there. Pollux has a staff branch dedicated entirely to investigate unfair advantages obtained from bugs, selfbots, macros, bot farming servers, and general spamming/flooding. As well as mechanisms to detect those and penalise cheaters on-spot. We enforce fair play so everyone can have fun without compromising the economy and leaderboards ecosystem.
            
        .col-block.service-item(data-aos='fade-up-left')
          .service-icon.service-icon--mobile-dev
            i.fas.fa-sun 
          .service-text
            h3.h4 Global Events! Only with Pollux 
            p And finally, unlike 100% of other bots, Pollux is the first (and so far the only) to provide Global events every so often. Events are unique periods where a specific theme is used to promote special hunting/collecting games, rewarding users with exclusive thematic cosmetics that are then rendered unavailable for the rest of the year, or even forever (these items does not count on the completionist %). 
      // end services-list
    // end s-services
