    section#info.s-blue
      //section.s-blue
      .row.section-header(data-aos='fade-up')
        .col-eight
          .col-full
            h3.subhead.subhead--light General Information
            h1.display-1.display-1--light
              | A bit more about this maid
          .row(data-aos='fade-up')
            .col-full
              p.lead
                | Pollux started as a semiprivate bot, originally for the Skynet Maid Cafe Server as a mascot. Within a few months Pollux was wandering around some other servers until she became public. 
              p.lead
                | As soon as she reached about 500 servers, in July 2017, a refactor featuring the first original design and the current Pollux we know today was made. And since then, her reputation and love has increased over the time.
              p
                | Pollux has been through a lot. But always keeping up and going. Pollux's development is slow due to its single-dev nature, but that also ensures it follows all the design principles strictly and also allows for a more robust way of implementing things.
              p
                |She's by any means a role model of her kind, but can be said is one of the few being constantly changed down to the core. 

